EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 181000Z TO 182000Z AUG
   WITHIN 30 MILES OF 57-37.9N 009-12.5W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR
   PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 1766/15(37), WRECK REMOVED.
3. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2000/15(37), AID RESTORED.
4. CANCEL THIS MSG 182100Z AUG 15.
